text: Lucerne-Land District is a new district of the Swiss canton of Lucerne. 81,592 people lived there in 31 December 2016. It includes only the city of Lucerne. == Mergers == On 1 January 2010 the municipality of Littau merged into the city of Lucerne. The district was created on 1 January 2013.
